				<img src="images/alliance.png" alt="alliance flag" class="ribbon">
				<h5>Onyx Marshall of House Matheredor.</h5>
				<p>A headstrong and brash Kaldorei hailing from the ancient forest of Val'sharah. While she certainly isn't one of the oldest Kaldorei, her martial prowess and Druidic skill speaks for itself. After spending countless years of her life dedicated to patient vigil and defense of her people's values, she now stikes out on her own.</p>
