			<p>Hafza is a now ancient Draenei, originally hailing from Argus. Much of her life was spent aboard the Genedar and vairous other worlds, all eventually brought to destruction by the Burning Legion. Now, without the worry of the Crusade, she can now focus on what really matters: friends and her family. Oh, and Mothy. Of course.</p>
		</div>
