			<h1>Evidori</h1>
			<img src="images/horde.png" alt="horde flag" class="ribbon">
			<h5>Spellblade and thief from Suramar.</h5>
			<p>Can you imagine spending your life within a domed city? Locked away from a world you believed destroyed, only to discover it was alive all that time? That your own kin now shunned you, and the newest of powers and faces welcomed you with open arms? Evidori asks herself these questions before dedicating herself to the Horde. To fighting for freedom, for safety, and so no city must suffer the same fate as Suramar did.</p>
		</dir>
		<dir class="card">
			<h1>Kelltaa</h1>
			<img src="images/alliance.png" alt="alliance flag" class="ribbon">
			<h5>Engineer in the Army of the Light.</h5>
			<p>The Army of the Light gave Kelltaa purpose. A drive. Something to rally behind like never before. Her life before the Xenedar is merely a page you skip before getting to the beef of her story. Now with the Burning Legion gone, she has found herself able to relax and focus on herself. At least, until the next big threat happens and demands her attention once more.</p>
